description: Retrieves the settings for the sensitivity inspection template for an account.

parameters.name: id
parameters.description: The unique identifier for the Amazon Macie resource that the request applies to.

nested_items.name: description
nested_items.description: The custom description of the template.

nested_items.name: managedDataIdentifierIds
nested_items.description: An array of unique identifiers, one for each managed data identifier to exclude. To retrieve a list of valid values, use the ListManagedDataIdentifiers operation.

nested_items.name: allowListIds
nested_items.description: An array of unique identifiers, one for each allow list to include.

nested_items.name: customDataIdentifierIds
nested_items.description: An array of unique identifiers, one for each custom data identifier to include.

nested_items.name: managedDataIdentifierIds
nested_items.description: An array of unique identifiers, one for each managed data identifier to include.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the template: automated-sensitive-data-discovery.

nested_items.name: sensitivityInspectionTemplateId
nested_items.description: The unique identifier for the template.
